snippet.title: Beggar's Paradise | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
My first Unity game!

Download for Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.CritterEntertainment.BeggarsParadise
Download for iOS - https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mobile-phone-mogul/id1668562784?platform=iphone

Due to some regulatory issues the game looks completely different for iOS, but the core mechanics are the same. I have spent lots of hours working on this and it would be of great help if you'd rate it in the store!

Music by - Lazz (https://open.spotify.com/artist/4ZoDgLUUzep4J2i47556l9?si=w-0ri6lGSe-EkBnL3WZO6g)
